[
  {
    "text": "We're finally tracking his signal again.",
    "start": 1.2,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "This is what we have been waiting for.",
    "start": 4.533,
    "duration": 2.066
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure the Tri-Titan is ready for deployment, Athena.",
    "start": 7.366,
    "duration": 3.566
  },
  {
    "text": "Time to put an end to this madness.",
    "start": 18.23,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Brother.",
    "start": 21.996,
    "duration": 2.233
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going in.",
    "start": 198.162,
    "duration": 1.166
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for your help, Athena.",
    "start": 199.861,
    "duration": 2.033
  },
  {
    "text": "Stay alert.",
    "start": 201.894,
    "duration": 1.233
  },
  {
    "text": "Things are unpredictable from here.",
    "start": 203.127,
    "duration": 2.366
  },
  {
    "text": "Hmm...",
    "start": 213.225,
    "duration": 1.567
  },
  {
    "text": "So this is where you've been hiding, brother.",
    "start": 214.925,
    "duration": 2.899
  },
  {
    "text": "Brother, can you hear me?",
    "start": 224.056,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "Your brother is gone.",
    "start": 225.49,
    "duration": 1.932
  },
  {
    "text": "Coming all this way to \"save\" him.",
    "start": 227.789,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Impressive.",
    "start": 229.689,
    "duration": 1.333
  },
  {
    "text": "But so very pointless.",
    "start": 231.022,
    "duration": 1.666
  },
  {
    "text": "Your brother is nothing without me.",
    "start": 232.688,
    "duration": 2.266
  },
  {
    "text": "That’s a lie.",
    "start": 234.954,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "He’s worth more than your entire leeching species.",
    "start": 236.254,
    "duration": 3.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't think I don't know what you are.",
    "start": 240.087,
    "duration": 2.299
  },
  {
    "text": "You survive by stealing what others build.",
    "start": 242.386,
    "duration": 2.799
  },
  {
    "text": "What they are.",
    "start": 245.686,
    "duration": 1.266
  },
  {
    "text": "Don’t pretend you’re a god.",
    "start": 246.952,
    "duration": 1.533
  },
  {
    "text": "YOU'RE A PARASITE!",
    "start": 248.485,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Brother, fight back!",
    "start": 255.25,
    "duration": 1.267
  },
  {
    "text": "You’re stronger than this!",
    "start": 256.517,
    "duration": 1.399
  },
  {
    "text": "I know you’re still in there!",
    "start": 262.082,
    "duration": 1.867
  },
  {
    "text": "Please...",
    "start": 264.549,
    "duration": 0.866
  },
  {
    "text": "WHY?",
    "start": 286.244,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "WHY DID YOU COME FOR ME!?",
    "start": 287.011,
    "duration": 1.333
  },
  {
    "text": "You were neglected, and cast aside.",
    "start": 288.844,
    "duration": 2.466
  },
  {
    "text": "But you left before you could show \nthem who you really were back home.",
    "start": 291.31,
    "duration": 4.666
  },
  {
    "text": "You always had your own way of thinking.",
    "start": 295.976,
    "duration": 2.666
  },
  {
    "text": "And it mattered!",
    "start": 298.908,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Everything you’ve built...",
    "start": 300.008,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "The inventions, the augmentations, the tech.",
    "start": 301.408,
    "duration": 3.099
  },
  {
    "text": "It matters.",
    "start": 304.507,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "You could be changing everything back home.",
    "start": 306.107,
    "duration": 2.766
  },
  {
    "text": "But this madness?",
    "start": 308.873,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "This isn’t proving your worth,",
    "start": 310.373,
    "duration": 1.766
  },
  {
    "text": "It’s burying it!",
    "start": 312.139,
    "duration": 1.533
  },
  {
    "text": "And what makes you think going back will be any different?",
    "start": 314.539,
    "duration": 2.732
  },
  {
    "text": "I came all this way to find you.",
    "start": 317.705,
    "duration": 1.933
  },
  {
    "text": "Because I never stopped believing in you.",
    "start": 319.638,
    "duration": 2.333
  },
  {
    "text": "Because this time, we show them...",
    "start": 321.971,
    "duration": 2.366
  },
  {
    "text": "Together.",
    "start": 324.337,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "But you have to come home, brother.",
    "start": 325.437,
    "duration": 2.132
  },
  {
    "text": "Please.",
    "start": 327.569,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you… ",
    "start": 329.102,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "For coming...",
    "start": 330.302,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "But we can’t go home.",
    "start": 332.135,
    "duration": 2.733
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 335.468,
    "duration": 0.933
  },
  {
    "text": "Why not?",
    "start": 336.401,
    "duration": 1.133
  },
  {
    "text": "The warp drives are stable.",
    "start": 337.534,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "We could be home in a few months!",
    "start": 339.034,
    "duration": 1.733
  },
  {
    "text": "That’s not the problem.",
    "start": 341.967,
    "duration": 1.666
  },
  {
    "text": "The beings I summoned…",
    "start": 344.033,
    "duration": 1.766
  },
  {
    "text": "They’re heading for Earth's administrators.",
    "start": 345.799,
    "duration": 2.466
  },
  {
    "text": "They’re the last line protecting what’s left \nof the humans on Earth.",
    "start": 348.532,
    "duration": 3.766
  },
  {
    "text": "If those things reach them...",
    "start": 352.731,
    "duration": 1.833
  },
  {
    "text": "I don’t even want to imagine the \npowers they could unleash.",
    "start": 355.431,
    "duration": 2.666
  },
  {
    "text": "And they won’t stop with Earth.",
    "start": 358.097,
    "duration": 1.899
  },
  {
    "text": "Our home…",
    "start": 359.996,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Could be next.",
    "start": 361.763,
    "duration": 1.499
  },
  {
    "text": "Then we stop them.",
    "start": 364.995,
    "duration": 1.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Together.",
    "start": 366.662,
    "duration": 1.166
  },
  {
    "text": "And when it’s over…",
    "start": 367.828,
    "duration": 1.733
  },
  {
    "text": "We go home.",
    "start": 369.561,
    "duration": 1.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Get in.",
    "start": 371.827,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "Let’s finish what I started.",
    "start": 373.36,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "The right way.",
    "start": 375.36,
    "duration": 1.133
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you all deeply for watching.\n -Virlance",
    "start": 401.288,
    "duration": 3.133
  }
]